label: Companies NDAs Form
description: Upload the signed NDA form (PDF format).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'NDA form is required').refine((val) => val.endsWith('.pdf') || val.includes('pdf'), 'File must be a PDF format')

label: Company Name
description: Provide the full legal name of the company.
validation: z.string().min(2, 'Company name must be at least 2 characters').max(100, 'Company name must be less than 100 characters').regex(/^[a-zA-Z0-9s&.,-']+$/, 'Company name contains invalid characters')

label: Logo
description: Upload the company logo (image file).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'Logo is required').refine((val) => /.(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|svg|webp)$/i.test(val), 'File must be an image (jpg, jpeg, png, gif, svg, webp)')

label: Industry
description: Select industry type (input details for Other).
validation: z.enum(['general', 'specific', 'other'], { required_error: 'Please select an industry type' })

label: Description
description: Provide a summary of the company.
validation: z.string().min(10, 'Description must be at least 10 characters').max(500, 'Description must be less than 500 characters')

label: Country of Operation
description: Select the primary country of operation.
validation: z.enum(['usa'], { required_error: 'Please select an industry type' })

label: Main Website URL
description: Provide the company's main website URL.
validation: z.string().url('Invalid website URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: TikTok URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid TikTok URL').refine((val) => val.includes('tiktok.com'), 'Must be a valid TikTok URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: LinkedIn URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid LinkedIn URL').refine((val) => val.includes('linkedin.com'), 'Must be a valid LinkedIn URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Facebook URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid Facebook URL').refine((val) => val.includes('facebook.com'), 'Must be a valid Facebook URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Instagram URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid Instagram URL').refine((val) => val.includes('instagram.com'), 'Must be a valid Instagram URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: X URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid X URL').refine((val) => val.includes('x.com') || val.includes('twitter.com'), 'Must be a valid X/Twitter URL').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Other URL
validation: z.string().url('Invalid URL format').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Team Members Profile
description: List team members with details.
validation: z.array(z.object({})).min(1, 'At least one team member is required')

label: Team Video
description: Upload a team video (max 2 minutes).
validation: z.string().refine((val) => /.(mp4|avi|mov|wmv|flv|webm)$/i.test(val), 'File must be a video format').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Team Standards
description: Describe the team's motto, culture...
validation: z.string().max(300, 'Team standards must be less than 300 characters').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Products & Services
description: List products or services with details.
validation: z.array(z.object({})).min(1, 'At least one product or service is required')

label: Patents
description: List patents with details.
validation: z.array(z.object({})).optional()

label: Awards
description: List awards with details.
validation: z.array(z.object({})).optional()

label: Investment Stage
description: Answer questions to determine your investment stage

label: Organization Chart
description: Upload organization chart (PDF, Excel, CSV).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'Organization chart is required').refine((val) => /.(pdf|xlsx?|csv)$/i.test(val), 'File must be PDF, Excel, or CSV format')

label: Department Details
validation: z.any().optional()

label: Valuation
description: Provide company valuation.
validation: z.string().regex(/^$?[d,]+(.[d]{2})?[KMB]?$/, 'Invalid valuation format (e.g., $1,000,000 or $1M)').min(1, 'Valuation is required')

label: Previous Balance Sheets
description: Upload previous balance sheets (PDF, Excel, CSV).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'Balance sheets are required').refine((val) => /.(pdf|xlsx?|csv)$/i.test(val), 'File must be PDF, Excel, or CSV format')

label: Previous P&L Statements
description: Upload previous P&L statements (PDF, Excel, CSV).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'P&L statements are required').refine((val) => /.(pdf|xlsx?|csv)$/i.test(val), 'File must be PDF, Excel, or CSV format')

label: Annual Audit Reports
description: Upload annual audit reports (PDF, Excel, CSV).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'Audit reports are required').refine((val) => /.(pdf|xlsx?|csv)$/i.test(val), 'File must be PDF, Excel, or CSV format')

label: Financial Details
description: Upload financial details (check fs_financials excel sheet).
validation: z.any().optional()

label: Customer Satisfaction Rate
description: Enter customer satisfaction rate.
validation: z.string().regex(/^d{1,3}%$/, 'Must be a percentage (e.g., 95%)').refine((val) => parseInt(val) <= 100, 'Percentage cannot exceed 100%').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Customer Retention Rate
description: Enter customer retention rate.
validation: z.string().regex(/^d{1,3}%$/, 'Must be a percentage (e.g., 90%)').refine((val) => parseInt(val) <= 100, 'Percentage cannot exceed 100%').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)
description: Enter customer lifetime value.
validation: z.string().regex(/^$?[d,]+(.[d]{2})?$/, 'Invalid CLV format (e.g., $500 or $1,250.50)').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Marketing Details
description: Upload marketing details (check fs_marketing excel sheet).
validation: z.any().optional()

label: SWOT Analysis
description: Upload SWOT analysis (PDF) or chat with GPT.
validation: z.string().refine((val) => val.endsWith('.pdf') || val.includes('pdf'), 'File must be a PDF format').optional().or(z.literal(''))

label: Strategy Chart
description: Provide strategy details (chart form).
validation: z.string().min(20, 'Strategy details must be at least 20 characters').max(1000, 'Strategy details must be less than 1000 characters')

label: Competitors
description: List competitors with details.
validation: z.array(z.object({})).optional()

label: Registration Documents
description: Upload multiple registration documents (PDF).
validation: z.string().min(1, 'Registration documents are required').refine((val) => val.endsWith('.pdf') || val.includes('pdf'), 'File must be a PDF format')

label: Ask vs Valuation
description: Enter the percentage of ask vs valuation.
validation: z.string().regex(/^d{1,2}(.d{1,2})?%$/, 'Must be a percentage (e.g., 10% or 10.5%)').refine((val) => parseFloat(val) <= 100, 'Percentage cannot exceed 100%')

label: Type of Investor
description: Specify the type of investor (optional).
validation: z.string().max(50, 'Investor type must be less than 50 characters').optional().or(z.literal(''))
